{"tid":2380832,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"原告變被告：美國投票系統公司控特朗普律師朱利亞尼誹謗","createTime":"2021-01-26T07:16:20.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-26T08:09:23.000Z","uid":289257,"like":3,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"2b145473c86f12e2af79b461d98f7a59b3aabcb1","tid":2380832,"uid":289257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T07:16:20.000Z","msg":"美國投票系統公司Dominion，入稟控告前總統特朗普的律師朱利亞尼，指控他誹謗公司涉及選舉舞弊，欺騙數以百萬計民眾，令他們相信公司偷竊選票，製造選舉結果，要求朱利亞尼賠償13億美元。<br />\n<br />\n公司在入稟狀表示，朱利安妮的言論是故意，並確實激起了憤恨，對公司造成巨大傷害。公司為保護受到騷擾及死亡威脅的員工，花費了56.5萬美元用於保安方面，今次訴訟是要為公司、員工及選舉程序站起來。<br />\n<br />\n美國仲黑暗過大陸<br />\n真係人類文明最大威脅<br />\n寧願中共打柒美國deep state<br />\n侵粉說對不對？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca31c6c808c06320fc9995c0bca1d178e1fd3b0a","tid":2380832,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T07:17:37.000Z","msg":"link呢"},{"pid":"af3ac0aface3e90715f1ecc20bd9159208a50dd2","tid":2380832,"uid":289257,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ca31c6c808c06320fc9995c0bca1d178e1fd3b0a","tid":2380832,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T07:17:37.000Z","msg":"link呢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T07:19:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/amp/international/2376329\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Famp%2Finternational%2F2376329&d=KsvwSKeUMZz4C4B35sIM%2BBjE8xiivR5AeW87zNloLfY%3D&h=c31e856b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/amp/international/2376329</a>"},{"pid":"6f2fa49c1583d619780117475a9a420409d44203","tid":2380832,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"af3ac0aface3e90715f1ecc20bd9159208a50dd2","tid":2380832,"uid":289257,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ca31c6c808c06320fc9995c0bca1d178e1fd3b0a","tid":2380832,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"20